  "reference_number": "RUS1682",
  "remarks": "\nMajor General Alexey Vyacheslavovich AVDEEV is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019. Major General AVDEEV is a member of the Armed Forces of the Russian Federation, he has held the position of Commander of the 3rd Motorized Rifle Division since Jan 2019. Major General AVDEEV is therefore an “involved person” per regulation 6(2)(a)(i) by “destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine” in that he works for the Government of Russia as a Major General of the Armed Forces of the Russian Federation, thereby fulfilling regulation 6(4A)(i). \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
